des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your PRIMERO smart home products, after connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "PRIMERO" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our "PRIMERO" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Google Play Store, Apple App Store or Amazon Appstore then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “PRIMERO” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “PRIMERO” skill, and you'll be navigated to “PRIMERO” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your smart home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
“Alexa, turn off the fan.”
“Alexa, increase the fan speed.”
“Alexa, turn on the TV.”
“Alexa, turn off the TV.”
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the plug.”
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to blue.”
